title: People share their most memorable moments from the Obama presidency
text:
People share their most memorable moments from the Obama presidency Watch | People share most memorable moments of Obama presidency 05:32 Our Foreign Staff , video source The White House 9 January 2017 â€¢ 11:55pm 
H igh-profile figures, activists and children are among the people who shared their fondest memories of Barack Obama's presidency and list what they believe were his biggest achievements. 
Aung San Suu Kyi , Leonardo Di Caprio and Kerry Washington were among the people reflecting on moments from Mr Obama's time in office that meant the most to them ahead of his departure from the White House.
